values: Wow... it was slow today at work. All I did was enter in the beeper numbers and run people there food, clean up every once in awhile... but most of all stood there blank-faced looking at the newspaper while drinking sodee pop. But I know it will be chaos tomorrow. The people there are cool lol. Especially Daimeon... he's hot lol. He made me mozzarella sticks when I got off work. Hehe.

Yeah, I know it was yesterday, but right now I feel like posting about it.

It's hard everytime father's day comes around... it's been about 6 years now since my dad has passed away... I really miss him and it's so hard to believe he's gone after all this time. He was the best dad any one could ever have. His personality and humor was loved by everyone. He'll always be apart of me and even though he isn't here to hear me say this I just want to tell him Happy Father's Day...

I got my hours today...I start training tomorrow. Here's my hours for now.

Monday: 11am-2pm
Tuesday: 11am-2pm
Thursday: 11am-2pm
Friday: 11am-2pm
Sunday 11am-2pm

That's what they are for now just until I learn how to do everything.

I got new black pants today also b/c our uniform is black pants and a t-shirt that they'll give me 2morrow. I'm really nervous for 2morrow. I hope I do ok!!!
HAPPY GRAD-GEE-WATION BUDDY!!!! Sorry I can't be there!! I feel so bad! Stupid cars. Anyways...hope you have a good one!! You, Brian, and Eric better behave!!! lol

Well I had Orientation today at BW3's. It was at stinkin 10 in the morning. There were 3 of us that were suppose to be there, but only 2 showed up. Me and this guy named Ryan. This other guy Dameon showed him and I around and had us fill out 2 papers. I get my work scheduale 2morrow, so I'll post it up on here lol.

I didn't go to church either today. My whole family and I aren't feeling too well. NOT GOOD! Well I'm gonna play The Sims some more. Boy I've been so lazy today. Might as well enjoy while I can before I start working!!

I *HEART* YOU! Thanks for being such a great friend... even thought we didn't get along too well throughout elementary, we were always best friends in the end and we always will be... Happy 17th birthday, I wish you the best!

Can't wait for the party tonight! woo!

WOOOOOOOO!!!! I'm awesome! Oh yeah! Well I got the job at BW3's if you can't tell lol! I'm so excited! *glad she finally has a life* I'll be making $6 or $6.50 being a greeter/food runner/ cashier.... myself and 2-3 other people will be switching jobs so things don't get boring. Orientation will be coming up (the lady's gonna call me) and we get shirts and all this junk! So I'm excited!!!
AHHH!!! I'm soooo nervous!! I have my interview today... I was told I'll deffinatly get it by my neighbor.... *crosses fingers* wish me luck!!!!

Yeah baby! 

This day was so boring....I sat on my lovely butt just like I'm going to do every day this summer unti l I get a car! 

Anyways I figured I'd do something productive, so I went and got my photos blown up in to 8x7's for our photography display this weekend and I took the movie my brothers, my best bud Nici and I watched last night back today (The Guru was so freaking hilarious and so disturbing at the same time!)... then I went in and got an application at BW3's since my neighbor knows the owner and everyone in there lol. And they said I have an interview tomorrow. My neighbor told me that I'll most deffinatly get it *crosses fingers*. I don't care, I need a job! I'm poor! *cries*

Well my interview is at 1 pm ....wish me luck!

This summer is going to suck so bad. I have no car to go anywhere, except for my moms. But that means I can't go visit friends more than 2 hours away, b/c we have to share the freaking car. My life sucks... i need money and a car.
I'm done venting.

YAY! GO JASON! He graduated friday! 

Jason came to my house thursday and spent the night and we left early friday. We went to his graduation (which is in VA). SO it was a pretty good weekend! I just got home today from there. So again Congrats Jas!
Why won't my stupid pictures ever show up!? They do every once in awhile! Someone help!

... and look how excited I look! I'm just so exhausted from exams! I did horrible on my spanish exam today, but good on the first part of it.. I hate spanish. I'll just speak spanglish if I ever need to talk to a spanish speaking person. I'll never use that languauge in what I want to do. No exams for me tomorrow, just sleeping in! Finally! Of course I'll have homework all summer for this extra math class I'm taking.. gah! I hate math too! lol. I'm so hateful. Just give me english and art classes the rest of my life! Please! Well I'm going to continue chatting online here! I'm going to the mall today with my family and my best bud, Nici... Hot Topic here we come! *giggles*

It's raining. A little more than it should. But it's comforting to sit here and watch it. I'm at school wasting away until summer break comes. Only today and tomorrow... and of course thursday for exams, but I only have to be here until 12:15. 

I'm leaving thursday after exams for VA. Jason's picking me up. I think he's nuts for driving almost 11 hours in one day, but he really wants me at his graduation, and i want to be there too. I'm not sure when I'll be back... possibly Monday or Tuesday. It's nice not to worry about the days as much with school letting out. 

Summer Plans:
- get a job
- make lots of money
- buy a good camera
- work on my website
- write more of my book
- read more
- go to Heritage for camp!
- go running or biking just about everyday
- go to Warped Tour!
- go camping the 4th of July
- visit the guys in cinci. 
- paint my room
- go skiing and jet skiing again
- sell my car and get a new one
- see some good movies
- go to FL?
- buy the new Rufio CD
... who knows what else. but that's what I'm going to try and do this summer, at least be productive and not waste away inside.

Today was such a long day. I actually had a life outside of the computer. My goodness I'm pathetic. I have a journalism exam to get done procrastination always gets me in trouble... It's due tomorrow and I've only got one page of the article done, well not even that *thinks of ways to b/s the whole assignment*...maybe if I make the test bigger? ...maybe...???

I'm sad right now and extremly tired. School is almost out. Three more days and one exam day, for me at least...

missing someone...

it's like... you can feel their presense on you, and that moment you can almost breathe, but only for a second, and all your pain goes away, b/c deep inside you know that that same person just might be thinking of you at the same time... and when it rains, you walk outside just and stand there to feel the rain falling on you, and you feel their tears and you know everything is right with them... that eventually you know u will see them again, maybe in ur dreams, or in reality, but whichever you know there will always be that feeling in ur heart that won't go away and that's what makes you miss them every second and it's a feeling so beautiful, but so horrifying at the same time b/c you have that urge to be with that person, to be one with them for just a moment... and to be with them would be such a rush and time would be lost within itself and you in each other...

yeah, I'm done... sleepy time..................night ZZZzzzz....
W00t! Finally I got a stinkin journal! I finally get to rant and rant and rant all day long. Yeah, this is short, but I have graduation parties to go to...so I will write more!
